\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\partial H}{\partial z}$
\end_inset

, 装满样品的样品管在非均匀磁场中要受到力的作用。
\begin_inset Formula $dz$
\end_inset

一段样品的体积为
\begin_inset Formula $Adz$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

为样品管横截面积。由(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:8-100"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

