\begin_inset Formula $\chi_{m}\cdot\frac{\rho}{M}$
\end_inset

为体积磁化率, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\chi_{m}\cdot\frac{\rho}{M}HAdz$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $dz$
\end_inset

高的样品柱的磁矩, 它所受的力为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
dF=\chi_{m}\frac{\rho}{M}HA\frac{\partial H}{\partial z}dz\label{eq:8-127}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

积分上式得到整个样品上所受的力
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
F=\int_{z_{H}}^{z_{0}}\chi_{m}\frac{\rho}{M}HA\frac{\partial H}{\partial z}dz=\int_{H}^{0}\chi_{m}\frac{\rho}{M}AHdH=\frac{\rho A}{2M}\chi_{M}H^{2}=\frac{k}{2}H^{2}A\label{eq:8-128}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

当样品周围介质的磁化率不能忽略时, 且样品管顶部磁场不为零而为
\begin_inset Formula $H_{0}$
\end_inset

时,  则
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
