\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\mu_{m\text{自}}=-g\mu_{B}\sqrt{s(s+1)}\label{eq:8-146}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

此自旋磁矩在外磁场方向 (
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

