\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
电子自旋磁矩和外磁场的相互作用能为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\epsilon=-\left(\boldsymbol{\mu}_{m\text{自}}\cdot\boldsymbol{H}\right)=-\mu_{m\text{自}}\cdot H=m_{s}\mu_{B}gH\label{eq:8-148}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

相邻磁能级的差为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\Delta\epsilon=\epsilon(m_{s})-\epsilon(m_{s}-1)=m_{s}\mu_{B}gH-\left(m_{s}-1\right)\mu_{B}gH=g\mu_{B}H\label{eq:8-149}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

